#: ../working-with-content/portlet-management/portlet-types.rst:88
msgid "Review List"
msgstr ""

# 8f8807d6d4a547f991354f7a0c85c496
#: ../working-with-content/portlet-management/portlet-types.rst:90
msgid ""
"The Review List Portlet will display a **list of objects that have been "
"submitted for review**. If you are using a submit and review cycle (and have"
" properly set global roles for your users) this is a great way for reviewers"
" to see what content has been submitted for review. This Portlet only "
"appears to those logged in as this state is not viewable to the public."
